{"tid":627417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專責委會拒放寬保密要求","createTime":"2018-04-13T03:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T03:16:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0897210ef861dfb656a6efc45633c5ab6004cb3b","tid":627417,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180413/20360097?_ga=2.69240720.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F20360097%3F_ga%3D2.69240720.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=0oCxB4PKUF1ZroO7ywWN2Bxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=a769dfee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F20360097%3F_ga%3D2.69240720.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=fee234b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180413/20360097?_ga=2.69240720.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n專責委會拒放寬保密要求<br />\n<br />\n3.3K<br />\n港聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180413/large/13ls2p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180413%2Flarge%2F13ls2p3.jpg&h=5b6c7b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁振英<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】調查民建聯周浩鼎與前特首梁振英私通一事的調查委員會，有意向調查梁振英UGL事件的專責委員會委員取證。UGL專責委員會主席謝偉俊雖指，委員是否向調查周浩鼎委員會作供，由委員自行決定，然而專責委員會不會放寬對委員的保密要求。有專責委員會的民主派委員表明不認同，因會令委員作供時受制，甚至令調查委員會得不到具體結果。<br />\n<br />\n謝在閉門會議後見記者，他說會議主要討論調查周、梁私通的調查委員會要求，並作兩個決定，包括專責委員會是否出席調查委員會聆訊，由委員自行決定，不過專責委員會不會放寬保密要求。謝解釋，由於一方面希望「盡可能配合各委員會嘅調查」，而同時專責委員會有保密要求，「所以兩種情況之下我哋作出平衡」。<br />\n<br />\n專責委員會委員專業議政梁繼昌對決定感失望，認為議員有道德和政治責任配合其他委員會調查工作，他會向調查委員會作供。<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n市民踴躍　林卓廷：研其他捐款方式<br />\n<br />\n港聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n西環集中營：捐錢者眾　林鄭難「扮盲」<br />\n<br />\n港聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n眾籌200萬元　本周可望達標民主黨擬赴澳洲查UGL案<br />\n<br />\n港聞 5小時前"},{"pid":"20af2987d5bb3173146c7f5d288c008ff9fb20b9","tid":627417,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:15:09.000Z","msg":"誓死保護689<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa08d06a8d71fec9ad340571ee8b1dbfa4f3362","tid":627417,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"樓主硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}